Insider Activity


Individual




Jeffrey H. Smulyan



Mr. Jeffrey H. Smulyan is Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer at Emmis Communications Corp., Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer at Emmis Operating Co., an Advisor at BIA Digital Partners, a Member at American Bar Association, a Member at Indiana State Bar Association, a Member at The Federal Communications Bar Association, and an Advisor at Catalyst Investors LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at Alma Mater, Inc. and University of Southern California.
Mr. Smulyan was previously employed as Chairman by The Central Indiana Corporate Partnership and Chairman by The Radio Advertising Bureau. He also served on the board at The Finish Line, Inc. and National Association of Broadcasters.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Southern California and a graduate degree from the University of Southern California Gould School of Law.



